casebody.data:
Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Friedman.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Friedman (1990), 56 Ohio St. 3d 69.]

(No. 90-1103 Submitted July 31, 1990 Decided December 12, 1990.) J. Warren Bettis, disciplinary counsel, for relator. Per Curiam.

Pursuant to Gov. Bar R. V(44), we hereby publicly reprimand respondent for his conduct. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur. Douglas, J., not participating.
